those two, killed a man to get revenge.

761
00:58:31,074 --> 00:58:32,141
Really?

762
00:58:32,208 --> 00:58:35,044
They killed the man
who had raped the girlfriend.

763
00:58:35,378 --> 00:58:39,215
They themselves killed the man
that they wanted gone from this world.

764
00:58:40,116 --> 00:58:41,684
Because they couldn't trust the law.

765
00:58:43,186 --> 00:58:46,189
You and I are like that, too.

766
00:58:49,792 --> 00:58:53,129
Even if you hate him enough
to kill him, don't.

767
00:58:53,696 --> 00:58:55,398
Then all the reasons will disappear.

768
00:58:55,999 --> 00:59:01,337
How bad a person Min Jun-guk is...
Why we hate him so much...

769
00:59:02,005 --> 00:59:03,339
It will all disappear.

770
00:59:03,873 --> 00:59:08,878
The moment we kill him,
we won't be victims, but common murderers.

771
00:59:11,214 --> 00:59:12,849
So...

772
00:59:13,783 --> 00:59:18,454
Don't even think about seeking vengeance
on Min Jun-guk.

773
00:59:18,955 --> 00:59:20,089
Okay?

774
00:59:25,028 --> 00:59:27,063
What are you doing? Answer me quickly.

775
00:59:29,966 --> 00:59:33,836
What if Min Jun-guk tries to hurt you?

776
00:59:40,677 --> 00:59:44,314
Don't do it even then.
I will protect myself.

777
00:59:46,049 --> 00:59:50,186
Don't ever say you'll kill Min Jun-guk
and forget about it.

778
00:59:57,427 --> 00:59:59,896
Your grades are too good
for you to become a murderer.

779
01:00:00,263 --> 01:00:04,334
You're lucky.
You can have your pick of universities.

780
01:00:11,874 --> 01:00:14,510
Will you keep my secret?

781
01:00:15,511 --> 01:00:18,181
If the fact that I lost
my gun gets out, I will...

782
01:00:18,348 --> 01:00:23,152
Why did you suspect
Park Su-ha might have taken it?

783
01:00:24,020 --> 01:00:28,191
It's because I saw his eyes
when he looked at the gun.

784
01:00:28,324 --> 01:00:30,593
Why? What was in those eyes?

785
01:00:36,199 --> 01:00:38,067
MYEONG IL SA
CELL PHONE LOCATION TRACKING

786
01:00:38,434 --> 01:00:41,404
